    stable 0.3.2
   require GConf WebKit
  category development
 attribute gnome new
    source $GNOME_URL sources/anjal/${VERSION:0:3}/anjal-$VERSION.tar.bz2
  homepage http://live.gnome.org/Anjal/
  estimate 150
      desc 'email-client for mobile devices
anjal is a email-client specially made for Netbooks & Mobile 
environments which has a very low resolution, power/CPU and memory.
For Keyboard shortcuts visit:
http://live.gnome.org/Anjal/KeyboardShortcuts'

